These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, lizard, chinchilla
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, disaster, mystery, zombie
1. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the ferret and the person watching disaster movies##2
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the ferret##7
4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Pet   | lizard | chinchilla       | turtle | ferret        |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery  | disaster | zombie        | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, apricot, eggplant, raspberry
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, victorian, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the victorian house and the person eating eggplant##7
2. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
3. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the victorian house and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Food     | eggplant | apricot       | raspberry         | lime     |
| House   | gothic-revival   | farmhouse | victorian | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, collecting, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, van, bike, airplane
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the motorbike##7
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is drawing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | drawing | dancing | collecting | woodworking  |
| Transport   | bike | motorbike  | airplane   | van |

