.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, bellflower, begonia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, october, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsrose is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who growsbegonia##7
3. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | iris | rose | begonia       | bellflower |
| Birthday   | july      | april   | october | february  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, bike, van
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse, cycling, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the snowmobile##7
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport         | bike | snowmobile   | van | car |
| Sport   | rowing      | lacrosse | handball      | cycling |

