.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cherry, strawberry, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, funk, classical
1. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the fan funk##1
2. the fan funk is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the fan metal is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
6. the fan classical is somewhere between the fan ambient and the fan metal##7
7. the fan funk is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food      | cherry | cranberry      | strawberry | grapefruit     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | classical | metal   | funk |

