4. the photographer is somewhere between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsaconite##7
5. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
6. the photographer is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower          | poppy    | marigold   | bellflower | aconite  |
| Job   | manager | dressmaker | photographer    | analyst |

