3. the manager is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the coach is somewhere between the manager and the bartender##7
5. the analyst is on the left of the bartender##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Job   | manager | coach | analyst | bartender |
| Sport           | cricket   | sailing    | skateboarding       | parkour  |

