2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating apple##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person who likes azure and the person eating nectarine##7
6. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Food           | corn | apple | zucchini | nectarine |
| Color   | azure         | white      | ivory | apricot            |

