2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who likes turquise##2
6. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person who's hobby is drawing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
