3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the german is not the bluemaster-smoker##6
5. the nigerian is somewhere between the game-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
