4. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
5. the fan ambient is somewhere between the fan d&b and the person eating lettuce##7
6. the fan ambient is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the fan punk##3

