4 different pets are kept: rat, fish, goat, turtle
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the turtle is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
6. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is sailing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Sport   | surfing | sailing | water-polo      | weightlifting |
