The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, writer, scientist
1. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the pilot and the person who likes chestnut##7
2. the pilot is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
4. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
5. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Color         | chestnut    | blue | pink     | azure |
| Job   | writer | scientist  | firefighter | pilot |

 